ate change resulting, primarily, from differences in the way that modelled global NPP responds to a changing climate. The simulations illustrate, however, that the magnitude of possible biospheric in{\_}uences on the carbon balance requires that this factor is taken into account for future scenarios of atmospheric CO2 and climate change},
