climatic state in the tropical Pacific Ocean, which
increased available atmospheric moisture, and (3) a
southward shift in the Intertropical Convergence
Zone (ICTZ), which allowed tropical summer storms
associated with the Australian summer monsoon (ASM)
to penetrate deeper into the southern part of the
