produced by a number of studies, particularly from
National Meteorological Services (NMSs). Hemispheric
temperature averages for land areas developed with
the new CRUTEM4 data set differ slightly from their
CRUTEM3 equivalent. The inclusion of much additional
data from the Arctic (particularly the Russian
