temperature and NA SSTs. However, the
teleconnections between NA and CEP SSTS and between
CEP SSTs and CUS temperature are poorly simulated
and the models produce substantially less NA SST
variability than observed, perhaps hampering their
ability to reproduce the warming hole.},
