5degreesN-5degreesS). Regression analysis allows a
more complete view of how the SSTs, outgoing
longwave radiation, precipitation, diabatic heating,
and atmospheric circulation respond with ENSO. The
second mode indicates aspects of the systematic
evolution of ENSO with time, with strong lead and
